Possible features to add:

- Servo motor to spin plant pot to get even amounts of sunlight.
- Thermistor to check for temperature values around the plant.
- Control of artificial lighting with photoresistor to detect how much natural light is present.
- Mobile app to give user information on plant's status and push notifications.
- Nutrient sensors to detect deficiencies in soil.
- Humidity sensors and control of misters to provide particular climates for specific plants.

Remember: This is a prototype! There is plenty of room for improvement!
